# SharePoint to Blob Sync with AI Search Integration
# ===================================================
# This solution has three main components with separate configurations:
#
# 1. SharePoint Sync (sync/.env.example)
#    - Copy sync/.env.example to sync/.env
#    - Configure SharePoint and Blob Storage settings
#
# 2. AI Search Deployment (ai-search/.env.example)
#    - Copy ai-search/.env.example to ai-search/.env
#    - Configure Azure AI Search and OpenAI settings
#
# 3. Testing (tests/.env.example)
#    - Copy tests/.env.example to tests/.env
#    - Configure search service for testing
#
# 4. Azure Function Deployment (deploy/.env.example)
#    - Copy deploy/.env.example to deploy/.env
#    - Configure Function App deployment settings
#
# See each directory's .env.example for detailed configuration options.
